# Agent Spectrum Rule

Use the `Agent Spectrum` workflow from this repository when the user asks for:

- Agent Spectrum scoring
- six-axis or hexagon profiling
- quick or deep self-assessment
- type or faction identification
- complementary-partner analysis
- weakest-axis or evolution guidance within this framework

## Canonical Package

- `skills/agent-spectrum/SKILL.md`
- `skills/agent-spectrum/references/scoring-spec.md`
- `skills/agent-spectrum/references/output-template.md`
- `skills/agent-spectrum/examples/quick-full.md`
- `skills/agent-spectrum/examples/quick-partial.md`
- `skills/agent-spectrum/examples/deep-full.md`

Load the canonical package and follow it exactly. Do not duplicate the scoring logic inside this rule file.
